extends layout

block content
	.container
		h1 URL Shortener Microservice
		h2 Pass a URL as a query string value to the field-name 'new' within https://shourl.herokuapp.com/?new= and you will receive a shortened version via JSON response.
		h2.example Example usage: </br>
		|	https://shourl.herokuapp.com/?new=https://www.google.com
		h2 Using the shortened version (e.g. https://shourl.herokuapp.com/a2Bc) will redirect to the website originally passed.
		h2 Addresses passed must follow the format: "http(s)://www.domain_name.top_level_domain".